flowchart TD
    Raw[(Raw time-series store\nFull resolution, 72h retention)] --> OneMin[1-minute rollup job\nMean / min / max / stddev / count]
    OneMin --> OneMinTable[(1-minute rollup table\n30-day retention)]
    OneMinTable --> Hourly[Hourly aggregation job]
    Hourly --> HourlyTable[(Hourly rollup table\n2-year retention)]
    HourlyTable --> Daily[Daily aggregation job]
    Daily --> DailyTable[(Daily rollup table\nIndefinite retention)]
    OneMin --> Quality[Data quality score\nSamples received vs expected]
    Quality --> QualityStore[(Quality metrics store)]
    OneMinTable --> OpsDash[Operational dashboard\nReal-time + recent history]
    HourlyTable --> ReportSvc[Reporting service\nScheduled PDF / CSV]
    DailyTable --> Warehouse[(Data warehouse\nBigQuery / Redshift)]
    Warehouse --> BizAnalytics[Cross-domain analytics\nIoT + production + maintenance]
    QualityStore --> OpsDash
    DailyTable --> Compliance[Compliance archive\nAudit records]
